# AI Social Media Automation using Make.com

## 🎥 Demo
[https://youtu.be/qir44V17MUE]

## ❓ Problem
Posting consistently on social media takes time and effort.

## 💡 Solution
Built an AI-powered system to generate and automate posts.

## ⚙️ Workflow
1. Input topic
2. Generate content using AI
3. Add hashtags automatically
4. Prepare post for publishing

## ⚠️ Challenge
Image automation was not completed due to storage/integration requirements.

## 🚀 Key Learning
Automation requires handling both data and media for full functionality.

## 📊 Use Cases
